422
00:28:31,091 --> 00:28:34,677
Dal-geon! Dal-geon, preber sa!

423
00:28:34,678 --> 00:28:36,730
Rýchlo zavolajte záchranku!

424
00:28:37,306 --> 00:28:40,558
Musíme ho zachrániť!
Dal-geon!

425
00:28:40,559 --> 00:28:41,934
Dal-geon, preber sa!

426
00:28:41,935 --> 00:28:44,770
